A tiny jQuery plugin, with minimal [semantic] markup, for generating ui tabs.

Usage

$('dl').tabs();

<dl>
	<dt><a href="">Your link title</a></dt>
	<dd>
		<p>Your content.</p>
	</dd>
	<dt><a href="">Your link title</dt>
	<dd>
		<p>Your content.</p>
	</dd>
</dl>


